<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body style="margin:0; padding:0;">
<div style="height: 60px; margin:0; padding: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #005F6C; padding-top:15px;">
  <img src="http://ceomba.co.kr/assets/site-logo.gif" style="display: block; height: 60px;margin:0; margin-left: 15px;padding:0;">
</div>

<div style="margin:0; padding:0; margin-left: 30px;">
  <p style="margin:0; padding:0; line-height: 130%; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom:30px;">
  안녕하세요, 기업 핵심인재를 위한 CEOMBA 입니다.<br>
  <%= @user.name%>님의 콘텐츠에 아래와 같은 댓글이 게시되어 알려드리며,<br>
  클릭하시면 쉽게 댓글을 확인하고, 답글로 소통하실 수 있습니다.<br>
  <br>
  <%= @user.name%>님의 답글로, 새로운 연결, 협업, 창조의 문화가 만들어집니다.<br>
  항상 저희 CEOMBA와 함께해주심에 감사드립니다.
  </p>

    <% if @user_comments.any? -%>
      <div style="margin:0; padding:0; font-size:15px;border-bottom: 1px solid #005f6c; height: 30px; width: 850px;">
        <div style="text-align: center;background-color:#1a1a1a; font-weight:bold;color:white; width:90px; height: 23px;padding:0;padding-top: 7px;float:left;">Members</div> 
        <div style="float:left; line-height:30px;margin-left: 10px;font-weight:bold;"><%= @user.name %>님의 프로필 페이지에 달린 댓글입니다.</div>
        <%= link_to "바로가기>>", professional_url(@user), style: "text-decoration: none; font-weight:bold;text-align: center;background-color:#005f6c; color:white; width:90px; height: 23px;padding:0;padding-top: 7px;float:right;" %>
      </div>

      <div style="clear:both; height:0"></div>

      <!-- 댓글 컨테이너-->
      <div style="margin:0; padding:0; padding-left: 50px;">

        <!-- 댓글 엔트리 개별 -->
        <% @user_comments.each do |comment| -%>
          <div style="width:800px; height: 70px; border-bottom: 1px solid #005f6c; padding-top:15px;">
            <div style="width:200px; height: 100%; line-height: 120%;float: left;">
              <span style="font-size:14px"><%= comment.user.name %></span><br>
              <span style="font-size:12px">
                <%if comment.user.company -%>
                  <%= "#{comment.user.company.name} #{comment.user.position}" %>
                <% else -%>
                  <%= comment.user.position %>
                <% end -%>
              </span><br>
              <span style="font-size:12px"><%= comment.created_at.localtime.strftime("%y.%m.%d. %I:%M%p") %></span>
            </div>
            <div style="width:600px; height: 100%;float: left;"><%= truncate(comment.content, length:100) %></div>
          </div>
          <div style="clear:both; height:0"></div>
        <% end -%>
      </div>
      <div style="clear:both; height:0"></div>
      <div style="height:70px">&nbsp;</div>
    <% end -%>

  <% @videos_and_comments.each do |talk, comments| -%>

    <div style="margin:0; padding:0;font-size:15px;border-bottom: 1px solid #005f6c; height: 30px; width: 850px;">
      <div style="font-weight:bold;text-align: center;background-color:#1a1a1a; color:white; width:90px; height: 23px;padding:0;padding-top: 7px;float:left;">영상</div> 
      <div style="font-weight:bold;float:left; line-height:30px;margin-left: 10px;"><%= talk.title %></div>
      <%= link_to "바로가기>>", talk_url(talk), style: "font-weight:bold;text-decoration: none;text-align: center;background-color:#005f6c; color:white; width:90px; height: 23px;padding:0;padding-top: 7px;float:right;"%>
    </div>

    <div style="clear:both; height:0"></div>

    <!-- 댓글 컨테이너-->
    <div style="margin:0; padding:0; padding-left: 50px;">

      <!-- 댓글 엔트리 개별 -->
      <% comments.each do |comment| -%>
        <div style="width:800px; height: 70px; border-bottom: 1px solid #005f6c; padding-top:15px;">
          <div style="width:200px; height: 100%; line-height: 120%;float: left;">
            <span style="font-size:14px"><%= comment.user.name %></span><br>
            <span style="font-size:12px">
              <%if comment.user.company -%>
                <%= "#{comment.user.company.name} #{comment.user.position}" %>
              <% else -%>
                <%= comment.user.position %>
              <% end -%>
            </span><br>
            <span style="font-size:12px"><%= comment.created_at.localtime.strftime("%y.%m.%d. %I:%M%p") %></span>
          </div>
          <div style="width:600px; height: 100%;float: left;"><%= truncate(comment.content, length:100)%></div>
        </div>
        <div style="clear:both; height:0"></div>
      <% end -%>
    </div>
    <div style="height:70px">&nbsp;</div>
  <% end -%>
  <div style="clear:both; height:0"></div>

  <% @posts_and_comments.each do |talk, comments| -%>

    <div style="margin:0; padding:0;font-size:15px;border-bottom: 1px solid #005f6c; height: 30px; width: 850px;">
      <div style="font-weight:bold;text-align: center;background-color:#1a1a1a; color:white; width:90px; height: 23px;padding:0;padding-top: 7px;float:left;">칼럼</div> 
      <div style="font-weight:bold;float:left; line-height:30px;margin-left: 10px;"><%= talk.title %></div>
      <%= link_to "바로가기>>", talk_url(talk), style: "font-weight:bold;text-decoration: none;text-align: center;background-color:#005f6c; color:white; width:90px; height: 23px;padding:0;padding-top: 7px;float:right;"%>
    </div>

    <div style="clear:both; height:0"></div>

    <!-- 댓글 컨테이너-->
    <div style="margin:0; padding:0; padding-left: 50px;">

      <!-- 댓글 엔트리 개별 -->
      <% comments.each do |comment| -%>
        <div style="width:800px; height: 70px; border-bottom: 1px solid #005f6c; padding-top:15px;">
          <div style="width:200px; height: 100%; line-height: 120%;float: left;">
            <span style="font-size:14px"><%= comment.user.name %></span><br>
            <span style="font-size:12px">
              <%if comment.user.company -%>
                <%= "#{comment.user.company.name} #{comment.user.position}" %>
              <% else -%>
                <%= comment.user.position %>
              <% end -%>
            </span><br>
            <span style="font-size:12px"><%= comment.created_at.localtime.strftime("%y.%m.%d. %I:%M%p") %></span>
          </div>
          <div style="width:600px; height: 100%;float: left;"><%= truncate(comment.content, length:100)%></div>
        </div>
        <div style="clear:both; height:0"></div>
      <% end -%>
    </div>
    <div style="height:70px">&nbsp;</div>
  <% end -%>
  <div style="clear:both; height:0"></div>

  <p style="margin:0;padding:0;font-size: 14px;line-height: 160%;"> 만약, 문제나 궁금한 사항이 있으시면 답신 메일로 알려주십시오.<br>바로 조치해 드리겠습니다.<br>CEO MBA 관리자<br>(tel) 02-512-1018<br>(web) <a href="http://www.ceomba.co.kr">www.CEOMBA.co.kr</a><br>(e-mail) ask@ceomba.co.kr</p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
